content:
I'm wondering what the thinking is on the current maximum withdrawals per slot.

The latest estimate from Capella specs is at 16: https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/blob/dev/specs/capella/beacon-chain.md (first screenshot)

The only other value I've seen thrown around is 8, from an old EthResearch comment: https://ethresear.ch/t/the-economic-incentives-of-staking-in-serenity/4157/10 (second screenshot)
